vanna thamizh &lt;unk&gt; is a 2000 tamil romantic comedy film written and directed by &lt;unk&gt; , produced by udhayanidhi stalin , and produced by ramoji rao . the film stars parthiban , sneha , vindhya and livingston in the lead roles , while vivek , ponvannan and ponvannan play supporting roles . the film , produced by &lt;unk&gt; , had musical score by deva and was released on 15 january 2003 .